# File: build files - backup/vendor.js.ab
# Purpose: Backup copy of the vendor JavaScript bundle preserved from a previous Grunt build
# Dependencies: [vendor.js.ab]

## Overview
A preserved copy of a previous `vendor.js` build artifact stored in the `build files - backup/` directory. Contains the same concatenated minified vendor JavaScript (jQuery, Angular, Angular modules, and all other Bower dependencies) as the root `vendor.js`, captured at a specific point in time as a rollback reference. Approximately 1.2 MB.

## Interface
No exports. A reference/archive file not loaded by the running application.

## Dependencies
- vendor.js.ab — the canonical source this was copied from

## Implementation Notes
- Paired with `build files - backup/vendor.css` as a complete build artifact snapshot
- File size: ~1.2 MB
- Not referenced by `app/index.html` or any build configuration
- Intended as a manual backup, not part of the automated build pipeline
